THERE might be a quick solution for those who wake up in the middle of the night thirsty but requires something stronger than water. PHIL from Beer Goals shared a video on YouTube saying their beer goals is to make a beer pillow to accommodate those who get thirsty in the middle of the night. BEER PILLOW allows you to drink your beer in the middle of the night without moving an inch. All you need to do is reach for the straw and enjoy your drink. Said Phil: “Our new #BeerGoals is to create a #BeerPillow to drink a beer in the middle of the night, all night long. Beer Goals will show you how to have the ultimate brew night sleep. #Beer”. 